======================================================================
 Class TSXtSrv -- Definition of an 'extended' Service-Definition.
 This definition is used to store traffic-services which are used
   within traffic- and activity-definitions.
 Type of service: 'A' or 'T' or 'A/T'
 ##TSXtSrv (Eyecatcher)
